@BastianQoU: No, Melira **does** prevent the counters from being placed on [Etched Monstrosity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Etched Monstrosity). I hate quoting rules because I hate sounding like a know-it-all, but this is somewhat important to learn due to Melira's abilities:  

*121.5. If a spell or ability refers to a counter being “placed” on a permanent, it means putting a counter on that permanent while it’s on the battlefield, or that permanent entering the battlefield with a counter on it.*  

Somebody get [Midnight Banshee](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Midnight Banshee) on her side, by the way. Those two will do work.
